#: desktop/org.gimp.GIMP.appdata.xml.in.in:15
msgid "The GIMP team"
msgstr "ທີມງານ GIMP"

#: desktop/org.gimp.GIMP.appdata.xml.in.in:16 desktop/gimp.desktop.in.in:4
#: app/about.h:25
msgid "GNU Image Manipulation Program"
msgstr "ໂປຣແກຣມຈັດການຮູບພາບ GNU"

#: desktop/org.gimp.GIMP.appdata.xml.in.in:17 desktop/gimp.desktop.in.in:6
msgid "Create images and edit photographs"
msgstr "ສ້າງຮູບພາບ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂຮູບຖ່າຍ"

#: desktop/org.gimp.GIMP.appdata.xml.in.in:19
msgid ""
"GIMP is an acronym for GNU Image Manipulation Program. It is a freely "
"distributed program for such tasks as photo retouching, image composition "
"and image authoring."
msgstr "GIMP ເປັນຄຳຫຍໍ້ຂອງ GNU Image Manipulation Program. ເປັນໂປຣແກຣມທີ່ແຈກຢາຍໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຟຣີສຳລັບວຽກຕ່າງໆເຊັ່ນ: ການແຕ່ງຮູບ, ການປະກອບຮູບ ແລະ ການສ້າງຮູບພາບ."

#: desktop/org.gimp.GIMP.appdata.xml.in.in:24
msgid ""
"It has many capabilities. It can be used as a simple paint program, an "
"expert quality photo retouching program, an online batch processing system, "
"a mass production image renderer, an image format converter, etc."
msgstr "ມັນມີຄວາມສາມາດຫຼາຍຢ່າງ. ສາມາດໃຊ້ເປັນໂປຣແກຣມລະບາຍສີທຳມະດາ, ໂປຣແກຣມແຕ່ງຮູບຄຸນນະພາບລະດັບມືອາຊີບ, ລະບົບປະມວນຜົນແບບຊຸດອອນລາຍ, ໂຕສະແດງຜົນຮູບພາບຈຳນວນຫຼາຍ, ໂຕແປງຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ຮູບພາບ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ."

#: desktop/org.gimp.GIMP.appdata.xml.in.in:30
msgid ""
"GIMP is expandable and extensible. It is designed to be augmented with plug-"
"ins and extensions to do just about anything. The advanced scripting "
"interface allows everything from the simplest task to the most complex image "
"manipulation procedures to be easily scripted. GIMP is available for Linux, "
"Microsoft Windows and OS X."
msgstr "GIMP ສາມາດຂະຫຍາຍ ແລະ ເພີ່ມເຕີມຄວາມສາມາດໄດ້. ມັນຖືກອອກແບບມາເພື່ອໃຫ້ສາມາດເພີ່ມສ່ວນເສີມ ແລະ ສ່ວນຂະຫຍາຍເພື່ອເຮັດວຽກໄດ້ເກືອບທຸກຢ່າງ. ສ່ວນຕິດຕໍ່ສະຄຣິບຂັ້ນສູງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ສາມາດຂຽນສະຄຣິບໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍຕັ້ງແຕ່ວຽກທີ່ງ່າຍທີ່ສຸດໄປຈົນເຖິງຂັ້ນຕອນການຈັດການຮູບພາບທີ່ຊັບຊ້ອນທີ່ສຸດ. GIMP ມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ໃນ Linux, Microsoft Windows ແລະ OS X."

#: desktop/org.gimp.GIMP.appdata.xml.in.in:48
msgid ""
"Scene 4 cut 15 of \"ZeMarmot\" being edited in GIMP. Illustration by Aryeom "
"(CC by-sa 4.0 International)"
msgstr "ສາກທີ 4 ຄັດທີ 15 ຂອງ \"ZeMarmot\" ກຳລັງຖືກແກ້ໄຂໃນ GIMP. ຮູບແຕ້ມໂດຍ Aryeom (CC by-sa 4.0 International)"

#: desktop/org.gimp.GIMP.appdata.xml.in.in:52
msgid ""
"Gull on beach photograph being edited in GIMP. Photo by Iana (CC by-sa 4.0 "
"International)"
msgstr "ຮູບຖ່າຍນົກນາງນວນເທິງຫາດຊາຍກຳລັງຖືກແກ້ໄຂໃນ GIMP. ຖ່າຍໂດຍ Iana (CC by-sa 4.0 International)"

#: desktop/org.gimp.GIMP.appdata.xml.in.in:56
msgid ""
"Portrait of Sofiia being edited in GIMP. Photo by Sofia (CC by-sa 4.0 "
"International)"
msgstr "ຮູບຄົນຂອງ Sofiia ກຳລັງຖືກແກ້ໄຂໃນ GIMP. ຖ່າຍໂດຍ Sofia (CC by-sa 4.0 International)"

#: desktop/org.gimp.GIMP.appdata.xml.in.in:60
msgid "Scanned engraving being edited in GIMP. Artwork by Liam (CC0)"
msgstr "ຮູບແກະສະຫຼັກທີ່ສະແກນແລ້ວກຳລັງຖືກແກ້ໄຂໃນ GIMP. ຜົນງານໂດຍ Liam (CC0)"

#: desktop/gimp.desktop.in.in:5
msgid "Image Editor"
msgstr "ໂປຣແກຣມແກ້ໄຂຮູບພາບ"

