#: app/sanity.c:546
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The configured filename encoding cannot be converted to UTF-8: %s\n"
"\n"
"Please check the value of the environment variable G_FILENAME_ENCODING."
msgstr "ການເຂົ້າລະຫັດຊື່ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຕັ້ງຄ່າໄວ້ບໍ່ສາມາດແປງເປັນ UTF-8 ໄດ້: %s\n\nກະລຸນາກວດສອບຄ່າຂອງຕົວແປສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ G_FILENAME_ENCODING."

#: app/sanity.c:565
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the directory holding the GIMP user configuration cannot be "
"converted to UTF-8: %s\n"
"\n"
"Your filesystem probably stores files in an encoding other than UTF-8 and "
"you didn't tell GLib about this. Please set the environment variable "
"G_FILENAME_ENCODING."
msgstr "ຊື່ຂອງໄດເຣັກທໍຣີທີ່ເກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າຜູ້ໃຊ້ GIMP ບໍ່ສາມາດແປງເປັນ UTF-8 ໄດ້: %s\n\nລະບົບໄຟລ໌ຂອງທ່ານອາດຈະເກັບໄຟລ໌ໃນການເຂົ້າລະຫັດອື່ນທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນ UTF-8 ແລະ ທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ແຈ້ງໃຫ້ GLib ຮູ້. ກະລຸນາຕັ້ງຄ່າຕົວແປສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ G_FILENAME_ENCODING."

